s_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Simone was sitting in her crystal-embellished leotard nervously waiting for her first score of the day, she soon discovered her \\\"huge\\\" mark of 14.733 and started beaming.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"JJ exclaimed: \\\"It's the highest beam score that we have seen today and those scores are just going to keep on coming because Simone Biles is back where she belongs.\\\"\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Inside Simone Biles' family life as Netflix series explores USA gymnast's past    Former sprinter Jeanette warned JJ to \\\"catch your breath\\\" as he was grinning from ear to ear over Simone's comeback success.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 887, \"end\": 894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7488893147117037e-14, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}, {\"begin\": 911, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9996648176505326, \"rank\": 0.0003350644518975662, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 949, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeanette_Biedermann\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2124993296378053e-12, \"text\": \"Jeanette\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeanette_B